AIFT-OS CLI

Truthful local-first federation operator CLI.

Usage:
  aift <command> [args]

Commands:
  bootstrap    active   Print federation bootstrap discovery JSON.
  federation   planned  Federation command group; planned until real APIs are proven.
  help         active   Show available commands.
  registry     active   Print command registry as JSON.
  repo         planned  Repository command group; planned until real APIs are proven.
  status       active   Inspect the real local repository status.
  verify       active   Run real local bootstrap verification checks.
  workflow     planned  Workflow command group; planned until real APIs are proven.
